<br />
<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">&nbsp; &nbsp;if&#40;&#40;Address&amp;0xF007&#41;&gt;=0x8000 &amp;&amp; &#40;Address&amp;0xF007&#41;&lt;=0x8007&#41;<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&#123;<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;VRC4_PRGUpdate&#40;&#41;;<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;return;<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&#125;<br /><br />&nbsp; &nbsp;if&#40;&#40;Address&amp;0xF007&#41;&gt;=0xA000 &amp;&amp; &#40;Address&amp;0xF007&#41;&lt;=0xA007&#41;<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&#123;<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;VRC4_PRGUpdate&#40;&#41;;<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;return;<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&#125;</div></div>

					
